name: Moonway
description: Moonway is a community-based token launched on 12 Nov 2021 and migrated to a new contract on Aug 16th, 2022. We've been around for a long time and aim for the Moon. A 7% tax is applied to all transactions, 2% of which are distributed to fellow Moonway holders. Another 2% tax is automatically added to a locked liquidity pool to generate an ever-rising price floor. 3% is sent for marketing. See more details at www.moonwaybsc.com
